name: Sadness and Loneliness
description:
A picture showing the play of black and white in the human mind. Thoughts that mix like a cocktail and lead to sadness. The loneliness of a handsome young man can only be compared to the loneliness of a tree in a techno-jungle. 

Location: Kharkiv, Ukraine
Date of photo creation: August 8, 2021
JPEG is 6000x4000 pixels
